kquote><br />\n學壞手勢啊， 到時連安全快門都唔識計"},{"pid":"1a1f632cb8570efe854834e44df8bdbc573f07e8","tid":396672,"uid":95241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T16:27:18.000Z","msg":"小弟本身有E-M5,之後買左X-E2就再無用過e-m5了<br />\n同級黎講omd係功能勁,但係影出黎既相我覺得富士岩我心水好多"},{"pid":"e521c277ee02bb93c6ceb99bcde1ec5afe83c46e","tid":396672,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T16:41:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟啱啱學既我怕我浪費左部xt20</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果新手我會揀em10ii, 因為個防震真係幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學壞手勢啊， 到時連安全快門都唔識計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n富士po有位巴打好似有依個問題，其實真係鍾意影相，影影下就會知多啲，我對比番2015同2017嘅相都覺得自己有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a369b7c1d66515da103a05472028c6aaa545aeba","tid":396672,"uid":52030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T17:23:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟啱啱學既我怕我浪費左部xt20</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果新手我會揀em10ii, 因為個防震真係幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學壞手勢啊， 到時連安全快門都唔識計</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n富士po有位巴打好似有依個問題，其實真係鍾意影相，影影下就會知多啲，我對比番2015同2017嘅相都覺得自己有進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n防震更大既作用反而係手持超遠程拍攝果陣減低取景搖晃程度(有時真係會搖到眼花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一般廣角到標變範圍會熄IS<br />\n利申:EM10 II用家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申2:一直都唔識計安全快門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申3:一直都係用直覺推ISO同快門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812c79e7cc4e963c0b0ca09f69fce3d4f63ac84f","tid":396672,"uid":116446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟啱啱學既我怕我浪費左部xt20</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果新手我會揀em10ii, 因為個防震真係幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學壞手勢啊， 到時連安全快門都唔識計</blockquote><br />\n巴打可唔可以講下咩係安全快門？"},{"pid":"1a077859395c52c424f78c37f1fa3f3cbfe5abd7","tid":396672,"uid":78399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:25:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>m43  鏡價堅嚇人</blockquote><br />\n邊支m43鏡貴過apsc??</blockquote><br />\n新果幾支真係貴，支12-100要八千幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難話貴定唔貴，睇返相近鏡頭<br />\n對返135底，姐係24-200mm f4<br />\nSony G lens 都係27-157.5mm f4 <br />\n都差左50mm"},{"pid":"bfaae97d9d8e915a0c4a7d3a7c446733bdfad504","tid":396672,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:28:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟啱啱學既我怕我浪費左部xt20</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果新手我會揀em10ii, 因為個防震真係幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學壞手勢啊， 到時連安全快門都唔識計</blockquote><br />\n有防震都可以識計，無防震想手持慢快門都難"},{"pid":"987f3f9e98fd8c61ad50b6f05a8c463dd2b72532","tid":396672,"uid":70553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:11:16.000Z","msg":"xt 20 witj 18 55 kit set夠你用<br />\n<br />\n安全快門 = 1/焦距<br />\n<br />\n用緊18mm   即係1 / 18 x 1.5 = 1/27<br />\n<br />\n快門唔可以慢過1/27 sec.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nISO auto也可  唯獨夜景要靚就較低d 落腳架"}]}